{
  "texts": [
    "This ensures that each chunk is a self-contained, semantically meaningful unit.",
    "The choice of chunking technique plays a vital role in balancing the need to capture full context while ensuring relevance in the retrieved information.",
    "Text-to-SQL translates natural language queries into SQL commands, bridging the gap between plain-text inputs and relational databases [Seabra et al., 2024b].",
    "This technique empowers users to access precise, structured data without requiring knowledge of SQL syntax [Liu et al., 2023].",
    "By leveraging LLMs, Text-to-SQL systems interpret natural language, map it to database schemas, and generate accurate queries."
  ]
}